title: 15 MIN DAILY STRETCH (full body) - for tight muscles, mobility & flexibility
description:
This is a quick, relaxing, full body stretch you can add into your daily routine! This 15 min stretch focuses on stretching tight muscles, and working on flexibility & mobility. Perfect to do first thing in the morning, before bed, or even after a workout. #fitness #yoga #homeworkout
